verbose_text: This integral analysis revealed that repeated administration of KP-54 resulted in a small but significant rise in LH (pre KP-54 10.8 +/- 1.8 versus post KP-54 13.4 +/- 1.6 IU/L, P = 0.038, XREF_FIG), with an equivalent elevation in serum estradiol levels across 21 days of KP-54 administration (pre KP-54113 +/- 9.7 versus post KP-54148.6 +/- 11.9 pmol/L, P = 0.029, XREF_FIG).
